These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
House: craftsman, cottage, townhouse, farmhouse
4 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, billiard, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, puzzles, sudoku
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the townhouse house is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the cottage house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 8. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| House          | farmhouse     | cottage   | craftsman | townhouse |
| Game   | bridge | monopoly    | scrabble   | billiard    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing       | card-games | sudoku  | puzzles      |

