.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, go, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, snowboarding, biathlon
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, musician, videographer, dressmaker
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing poker##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person playing billiard##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
11. the journalist is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Game      | billiard       | poker | chess     | go     |
| Sport   | volleyball      | surfing       | biathlon | snowboarding |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Job     | dressmaker | videographer     | journalist     | musician       |

