.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, pumpkin, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, japanese, nigerian, malaysian
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, trike, subway
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, chess, bridge
 1. the nigerian is on the right of the indian##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 4. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the person playing bridge is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the trike##2
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 9. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the nigerian is the person playing billiard##1
12. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | pumpkin      | plum   | apricot |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian | japanese | malaysian  |
| Transport   | roller   | trike         | motorbike  | subway  |
| Game           | chess      | billiard          | bridge | mah-jongg  |

