.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, tram, van
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, cooking, gardening, puzzles
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, davidoff, swisher, old-henry
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 4. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Transport           | ship    | van   | tram | motorbike |
| Hobby   | puzzles      | cooking    | traveling        | gardening         |
| Cigar         | alhambra    | swisher | old-henry         | davidoff    |

