4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, chinchilla, lizard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip, poppy, amaryllis
 1. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 6. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
| Beverage         | water | almond-milk    | milk | tea  |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | disaster   | zombie       | martial-arts |
