 3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 5. the tower house is the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the right of the tower house##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 8. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 9. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
10. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
11. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
12. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
13. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5

