The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, bus, snowmobile
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, mah-jongg, go
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person playing chess is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person playing go##2
 4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 6. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person playing chess is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
12. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| City      | boston   | marseilles | prague   | colone          |
| Transport          | airplane    | snowmobile        | bus     | helicopter          |
| Game           | billiard | mah-jongg        | chess | go |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

