.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
City: miami, boston, liverpool, hamburg
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, camping, collecting, writing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, sprite, juice
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
11. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
12. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| City          | miami | liverpool  | hamburg    | boston       |
| Hobby           | camping  | writing | collecting | fishing  |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | sprite   | juice  | tea     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 